  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Europe multi-centre holidays</h2>
<p>Step up your travel game with a multi-centre holiday. With the chance to discover and experience multiple destinations in one trip, you'll be able to walk your way through a variety of cultures, sights, and adventures.</p>
<p><img style="width: 848px; height: 451px;" src="/media/13095461/florence-multicentre-holiday.jpg?width=848&amp;height=451&amp;mode=max" alt="multicentre holidays europe" data-udi="umb://media/ac44788836594e5ab4acf5d4f9eb2bbd" /></p>
<p>Why limit yourself to one walking trail when you can conquer many on a multi-centre walking holiday? Experience the diverse terrains of multiple destinations, from the majestic mountains of the Swiss Alps to the serene lakes of <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a> and cultural hotspots of <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a>. Our multi-centre holidays offer a unique blend of natural wonders and cultural marvels that are sure to satisfy the adventurer within.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193}" title="Contact Us">Contact us today</a> to start planning your dream getaway. Our team is on hand to create a bespoke trip that’s perfect for you.</p>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: left;"><span><strong>For more information please call: <a href="tel:01483 791 111" class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111</a></strong></span></h3>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Our Multi-Centre Holidays</h2>
</div>
<h2> </h2>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;"><a name="backtotop"></a>Switzerland &amp; France<br />The Iconic Mountains Tour</h3>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/1451b25f07c546c09f3585c3c9a54203" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1451b25f07c546c09f3585c3c9a54203}" title="Iconic Mountains Tour"><img src="/media/13080454/zermatt-for-web.jpg?width=307&amp;height=165&amp;mode=max" alt="" width="307" height="165" data-udi="umb://media/ce2bd8338fbb4fd5b976bffdba2a1609" /></a><br /></strong></p>
<p>Spend an awe-inspiring week in two iconic resorts <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a>. Dominated by the majestic peaks of Mont Blanc and the Matterhorn, with stunning views.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/1451b25f07c546c09f3585c3c9a54203" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1451b25f07c546c09f3585c3c9a54203}" title="Iconic Mountains Tour" class="c-btn">Learn more</a></div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Italy<br />Venice &amp; Lake Garda</h3>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/e3a120dbe00143a4a6a5d16eab765959" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e3a120dbe00143a4a6a5d16eab765959}" title="Venice &amp; Lake Garda"><img src="/media/13080455/venice-gondola-for-web.jpg?width=307&amp;height=165&amp;mode=max" alt="" width="307" height="165" data-udi="umb://media/aebd38117ba34118ab4759d2a541c24d" /></a><br /></strong></p>
<p>Take in one of Europe’s most beautiful and romantic cities with a few night's spent exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7}" title="Venice">Venice</a> before relaxing on Italy’s <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">largest lake</a> on this popular twin centre holiday.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/e3a120dbe00143a4a6a5d16eab765959" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e3a120dbe00143a4a6a5d16eab765959}" title="Venice &amp; Lake Garda" class="c-btn">Learn more</a></div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Slovenia<br />Discover the Julian Alps</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553}" title="Discover the Julian Alps"><img src="/media/13080453/bohinj-for-web.jpg?width=310&amp;height=166&amp;mode=max" alt="" width="310" height="166" data-udi="umb://media/e27db2b616634b03968f5c0a921883b3" /></a><br /><span></span></p>
<p><span>Explore magnificent landscapes, dramatic scenery and the varied flora &amp; fauna of the Julian Alps by visiting three resorts surrounded by this wonderful mountain range.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0191268612e4a3389b47a26550db553}" title="Discover the Julian Alps" class="c-btn">Learn more</a></div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Italy<br />Venice, Florence &amp; Rome</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3}" title="Venice, Florence &amp; Rome"><img src="/media/13080462/florence-for-web.jpg?width=307&amp;height=165&amp;mode=max" alt="" width="307" height="165" data-udi="umb://media/3296fa18ba864c2c931ddd517f0e06e2" /></a><br /><span></span></p>
<p><span>This ultimate city break lets you discover Italy’s three most iconic cities in just one trip. High speed rail connections make it easy and enjoyable to combine Italy’s best cities.  </span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3}" title="Venice, Florence &amp; Rome" class="c-btn">Learn more</a></div>
<div class="g4" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Italy<br />Lake Como &amp; Milan</h3>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5}" title="Milan &amp; Lake Como"><img src="/media/13080458/lake-como-for-web-x1.jpg?width=307&amp;height=165&amp;mode=max" alt="" width="307" height="165" data-udi="umb://media/3f46fe72fded40019843b9ace60be315" /></a><br /></strong></p>
<p>Relax on the ink-blue waters of <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a> where the shores are lined with palatial villas and chic cafés before heading to the <a data-udi="umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd}" title="Milan">Milan</a>, the fashion capital of Italy for a spot of shopping and sightseeing.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5}" title="Milan &amp; Lake Como" class="c-btn">Learn more</a></div>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Book your dream multi-centre holiday today</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Don't miss out on a walking adventure of a lifetime. Book your multi-centre holiday today and discover the wonders of multiple destinations in one trip. </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>For more information please call: <a href="tel:01483 791 111" class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111</a></strong></span></h3>
